<plot>A string of random events control and connect the lives of three immigrants in the Silicon Valley - Arun, a South Indian Brahmin engineer with a middle class background... Kris, a flamboyant engineer body-shopped to the US... and Abbie, an illegal immigrant involved in drug trafficking. The story revolves around Arun's relationship with his US born wife, Dr. Lakshmi and the challenges that they face, adding up to the inevitable but surprise ending.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?412783</url></doc>
